  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/FSKit\/FSItem\/Attributes\/addedTime\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T15:46:35Z\n---\n\n# addedTime\n\n**Instance Property**\n\nThe item’s added time.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nvar addedTime: timespec { get set }\n```\n\n## Discussion\n\nThis property represents the time the file system added the item to its parent directory.\n\n## Working with time attributes\n\n- **accessTime**: The item’s last-accessed time.\n- **modifyTime**: The item’s last-modified time.\n- **changeTime**: The item’s last-changed time.\n- **birthTime**: The item’s creation time.\n- **backupTime**: The item’s last-backup time.\n\n",
